                    <physDesc>
                        <objectDesc>
                            <supportDesc>
                                <support><p>Large fragment of a cyrstalline white marble, intact along the upper edge, broken left and below, and upper right corner. Note that the right edge is a very clean edge, suggesting that this is the end of the slab in question, with a further slab adjoining. Finished on the reverse; the upper rear edge is chipped. </p>
                                    <material ana="#material.stone.marble" ref="http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/material/lod/48.html">marble</material>
