            <div type="apparatus" resp="#JP">
                <listApp>
                    <app><note>Text from autopsy</note></app>
                    <app loc="1"><note>It is obviously impossible to know the inflected form of Caesar</note></app>
                    <app loc="2"><note>The letter is either I, or N, or L; given the position at the end of the slab, I or N seems more likely than L</note></app>
                </listApp>
            </div>
            <div type="translation">
                <p><!--translation(s) - add @xml:lang for 'en' or 'it' to div--></p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>It would be tempting to associate the fragment, which seems likely to be part of a monumental imperial building inscription, with the early Imperial creation of a porticoed square in front of the great altar.</p>
            </div>
